title: BRIEF-Federated National Entered Reimbursement Contract With The State Board Of Administration Of Florida For 2018-2019 Hurricane Season
text: March 2, 2018 / 1:44 PM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Federated National Entered Reimbursement Contract With The State Board Of Administration Of Florida For 2018-2019 Hurricane Season Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 2 (Reuters) - Federated National Holding Co: * FEDERATED NATIONAL HOLDING - UNITS ENTERED REIMBURSEMENT CONTRACT WITH THE STATE BOARD OF ADMINISTRATION OF FLORIDA FOR 2018-2019 HURRICANE SEASON * FEDERATED NATIONAL HOLDING-THE CONTRACTS ARE PAYABLE IN 3 PREMIUM INSTALLMENTS DUE AUGUST 1, 2018, OCTOBER 1, 2018, AND DECEMBER 1, 2018 - SEC FILING Source text for Eikon:
